# SIDM2 Project Rules

## Available Resources
- Project documentation in /docs/*.md files - ALWAYS check these first
- TDZ C64 Knowledge server available via MCP - use c64-knowledge:search_docs for technical references
- Architecture overview in ARCHITECTURE.md
- API documentation in API.md

## Workflow
